===Specifications=== *[[ASUS DSL-N10]] (rev A1) - N150 Wi-Fi ADSL Modem Router <!-- :Router CPU: [[Ralink]] RT3050F @320MHz WiSoC • [http://www.natthapol89.com/2014/04/asus-dsl-n10-a1.html Spec.] :Router RAM: [[Winbond]] W9825G6JH-6 32MB (SDRAM) :Router Flash: ''Macronix'' MX25L3206EM2I-12G 4MB (SPI) :ADSL CPU: [[TrendChip]] TC3162LE-LQ128G (ADSL2+ Annex A) :ADSL RAM: [[Winbond]] W9816G6IH-6 2MB (SDRAM) :ADSL Flash: ''Macronix'' MX25L8006EM2I-12G 1MB (SPI) :ADSL Chip: [[TrendChip]] TC3086 (-QFN64-EPG) --> :CPU/ADSL: [[TrendChip]] TC3162LE; 1MB Flash, 2MB SDRAM :CPU/Wi-Fi: [[Ralink]] RT3050; 4MB Flash, 32MB SDRAM *[[ASUS DSL-N10 rev B1]] - N150 Wi-Fi ADSL Modem Router :CPU/ADSL: [[TrendChip]] TC3162LEM; 1MB Flash, 2MB SDRAM :CPU/Wi-Fi: [[Ralink]] RT3050; 4MB Flash, 32MB SDRAM *[[ASUS DSL-N10 rev C1]] - N150 Wi-Fi ADSL Modem Router :CPU/ADSL: [[Ralink]] RT63365; 8MB Flash, 32MB DDR RAM :Wi-Fi: [[Ralink]] RT5390; 12V w/ max. 0.5A current :Antenna: Fixed 2dBi (EU) or 5dBi (APAC) *[[ASUS DSL-N10E]] - N150 Wi-Fi ADSL Modem Router :CPU/ADSL: [[Realtek]] RTL8672VK; Flash: 2MB, RAM: 8MB :Wi-Fi: [[Realtek]] RTL8188RE; 12V w/ max. 0.8A current :Antenna: Fixed 2dBi (EU) or 5dBi (APAC)
